<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About TorqueX</title>

  <!-- Google Font -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN -->
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>

  <!-- Custom CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-900">

  <%- include('./partials/header') %>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">About TorqueX</h1>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12">
      <!-- Left Column -->
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center space-y-6">
        <!-- Image with overlay -->
        <div class="relative w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <img 
            src="https://www.shutterstock.com/image-photo/vertical-photo-headlight-modern-prestigious-600nw-1947016213.jpg" 
            alt="Luxury vehicle fleet" 
            class="w-full h-40 md:h-64 lg:h-80 object-cover transition duration-300 hover:scale-105" 
            onerror="this.src='/images/placeholder.jpg'; this.onerror=null;"
          >
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/30 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 text-white">
            <p class="text-lg font-medium">Premium Fleet Experience</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mission Card -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 w-full">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800 flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
            Our Mission
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            At TorqueX, our mission is to provide exceptional vehicle rental experiences that exceed our customers' expectations. We believe in offering premium vehicles at competitive prices, backed by outstanding customer service.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We strive to make the rental process as seamless as possible, from browsing our selection to returning your vehicle, ensuring that your journey is as enjoyable as your destination.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-400">
            <p class="text-blue-800 font-medium">
              "Your journey begins with the perfect ride"
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column -->
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex flex-col space-y-8">
        <!-- Our Story -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800 flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
            </svg>
            Our Story
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Founded in 2025, TorqueX was born from a passion for automobiles and a desire to revolutionize the car rental industry. We identified a gap in the market for a premium rental service that offered luxury and performance vehicles without the premium price tag.
            </p>
            <p>
              Starting with just a handful of vehicles, we have grown our fleet to include a diverse range of cars, SUVs, and specialty vehicles to suit every need and preference.
            </p>
            <p>
              Today, we serve thousands of customers across the country, providing them with unforgettable driving experiences and exceptional service.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
            <div class="p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">500+</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Vehicles</div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-600">10K+</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Happy Customers</div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600">5</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Years Experience</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Why Choose TorqueX -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800 flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z"></path>
            </svg>
            Why Choose TorqueX?
          </h2>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-200">
              <div class="bg-green-100 p-1 rounded-full mr-3 mt-1">
                <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="font-medium">Premium vehicles at competitive prices</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-200">
              <div class="bg-green-100 p-1 rounded-full mr-3 mt-1">
                <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="font-medium">Flexible rental periods with no hidden fees</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-200">
              <div class="bg-green-100 p-1 rounded-full mr-3 mt-1">
                <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="font-medium">24/7 customer support</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-200">
              <div class="bg-green-100 p-1 rounded-full mr-3 mt-1">
                <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="font-medium">Convenient pickup and drop-off locations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-200">
              <div class="bg-green-100 p-1 rounded-full mr-3 mt-1">
                <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="font-medium">Regular maintenance and safety checks on all vehicles</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <br><br><br>

    <!-- Meet Our Team -->
    <div class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-gray-800">Meet Our Team</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <!-- Team Member 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-blue-100">
            <img src="https://www.shutterstock.com/image-photo/happy-handsome-young-indian-man-260nw-2315729087.jpg" alt="CEO" class="w-full h-full object-cover" onerror="this.src='/images/placeholder-profile.jpg'; this.onerror=null;">
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Mr. Akshit</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-600 mb-3 font-semibold">CEO & Founder</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Automotive enthusiast with over 15 years of experience in the luxury car industry.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Team Member 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-green-100">
            <img src="https://www.shutterstock.com/image-photo/portrait-serious-confident-indian-man-260nw-2424906587.jpg" alt="Operations Director" class="w-full h-full object-cover" onerror="this.src='/images/placeholder-profile.jpg'; this.onerror=null;">
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Mr. Anirudh Sharma</h3>
          <p class="text-green-600 mb-3 font-semibold">Operations Director</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Logistics expert ensuring our fleet is always in top condition and ready for our customers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Team Member 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-purple-100">
            <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/474x/14/18/ae/1418ae90272105ea599c6f931a1b7aac.jpg" alt="Customer Service Manager" class="w-full h-full object-cover" onerror="this.src='/images/placeholder-profile.jpg'; this.onerror=null;">
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Mr. Ravinder</h3>
          <p class="text-purple-600 mb-3 font-semibold">Customer Service Manager</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Dedicated to ensuring every customer has an exceptional experience with TorqueX.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include('./partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>
